the%202018%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20won%20100%20seats%2C%20one%20short%20of%20the%20halfway%20mark.%20The%20BJP%20had%20suffered%20heavy%20losses%20compared%20to%20its%202013%20show%2C%20its%20seat%20tally%20dropping%20from%20163%20to%2073.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAshok%20Gehlot%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20support%20of%20Independent%20and%20BSP%20MLAs.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20six%20BSP%20MLAs%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20cementing%20its%20majority%20in%20the%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20faced%20a%20tough%20challenge%20in%202020%20when%20then%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Sachin%20Pilot%20led%20a%20rebellion%20which%20threatened%20to%20topple%20the%20government.%20Swift%20intervention%20by%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20saved%20the%20day.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%2C%20infighting%20and%20power%20tussle%20within%20the%20ranks%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20key%20challenge%20as%20the%20party%20gears%20up%20for%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInfighting%20is%20a%20key%20challenge%20for%20the%20BJP%20too%2C%20with%20rivals%20camps%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20jostling%20with%20each%20other%20for%20prominence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20about%20two%20decades%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20into%20the%20polls%20in%20Rajasthan%20without%20projecting%20Ms%20Raje%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20camp%20had%20been%20demanding%20that%20she%20be%20announced%20as%20the%20party's%20face%20for%20the%20election%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20statement%20that%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20face%20will%20be%20its%20lotus%20symbol%20put%20matters%20at%20rest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20countdown%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20flagging%20in%20particular%20the%20crimes%20against%20women.%20The%20ruling%20Congress%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20questioning%20the%20BJP's%20silence%20on%20such%20crimes%20in%20the%20states%20it%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696837440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F33ilm3pg_ashok-gehlot-pm-modi-pti-650_650x400_02_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-votes-in-single-phase-on-november-23-result-on-december-3-4463364%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20200%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20a%20single-phase%20on%20November%2023%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20today%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-votes-in-single-phase-on-november-23-result-on-december-3-4463364%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-votes-in-single-phase-on-november-23-result-on-december-3-4463364%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-votes-in-single-phase-on-november-23-result-on-december-3-4463364%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThey%20Had%20Wicket%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Smith's%20Blunt%20Spinners%20Remark%20After%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBowled%20out%20for%20199%20in%20their%20high-profile%20World%20Cup%20opener%2C%20Steve%20Smith%20admitted%20that%20the%20Australian%20batters%20failed%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20the%20Indian%20spinners%20on%20a%20tacky%20Chepauk%20surface.%20Opting%20to%20bat%20first%20in%20a%20surprise%20move%2C%20Australia%20were%20sitting%20pretty%20at%20110%20for%20two%20before%20left-arm%20spinner%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20(3%2F38)%20triggered%20a%20collapse%20with%20his%20triple%20blows%20in%20the%20middle%20overs.%20The%20total%20proved%20to%20be%20too%20less%20as%20India%20romped%20home%20with%20six%20wickets%20and%20nine%20overs%20to%20spare%20for%20a%20fine%20start%20to%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20their%20spinners%20bowled%20really%20nicely.%20Obviously%2C%20they%20had%20the%20wicket%20to%20suit%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said%20in%20the%20mixed%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20challenging%20against%20the%20spin%20since%20they%20are%20all%20very%20quality%20spinners.%20They%20really%20worked%20well%20together%2C%20and%20we%20struggled%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%20Besides%20Jadeja%2C%20wrist%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20picked%20up%20two%20wickets%20while%20there%20was%20one%20wicket%20for%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20India%20rode%20on%20Virat%20Kohli's%2085%20and%20KL%20Rahul's%20unbeaten%2097-run%20knock%20to%20complete%20the%20task%20in%2041.2%20overs%2C%20having%20recovered%20from%202%2F3%20in%20the%20second%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESmith%20credited%20Kohli%20and%20Rahul%20for%20their%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20game%20on.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20couldn't%20take%20it.%20Virat%20and%20Rahul%20played%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20composure.%20They%20played%20really%20smart%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20a%20kind%20of%20wicket%20where%20you%20could%20just%20muscle%20it%20and%20hit%20boundaries%20everywhere.%20Since%20they%20were%20chasing%20only%20200%2C%20they%20could%20take%20a%20bit%20more%20time%2C%20just%20play%20themselves%20in%2C%20which%20they%20probably%20needed%20to%20after%20being%20three%20down%20early%20on%20and%20build%20a%20partnership%20that%20they%20did%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%20Talking%20about%20the%20challenge%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20tricky%20wicket%20to%20bat%20on%2C%20while%20bowling%20under%20the%20lights%20with%20the%20dew%20around%20made%20it%20tough.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20challenging%20wicket%2C%20and%20we%20also%20saw%20a%20fair%20bit%20of%20spin%20taking%20place%2C%20along%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20movement%20for%20the%20seam%20bowlers%20off%20the%20cracks.%20So%2C%20obviously%2C%20it%20was%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B200%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20under%20par.%20Had%20we%20gone%20up%20and%20posted%20250%2C%20we%20would%20have%20been%20in%20for%20an%20interesting%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20the%20dew%20came%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20making%20it%20a%20bit%20easier%20to%20bat.%20We%20can't%20predict%20it%2C%20but%20we%20had%20three%20early%20wickets%20and%20also%20could%20have%20had%20possibly%20a%20fourth.%26quot%3B%20Smith%20was%20the%20top-scorer%20for%20the%20Aussies%2C%20making%20a%2071-ball%2046.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20his%20batting%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20playing%20quite%20nicely.%20I%20had%20to%20sort%20of%20work%20my%20way%20through%20to%20keep%20the%20runs%20coming%20on%20this%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFelt%20like%20I%20was%20moving%20along%20nicely%2C%20hitting%20a%20few%20nice%20drives%20to%20the%20fast%20bowlers%20and%20spinners.%20But%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20bigger%20one.%26quot%3B%20Up%20next%20for%20Australia%20will%20be%20South%20Africa%2C%20who%20got%20off%20to%20a%20blazing%20start%20with%20a%20102-run%20thrashing%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20Delhi%2C%20having%20posted%20a%20record%20total%20of%20428%20for%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESmith%20remarked%20that%20while%20the%20Lucknow%20wicket%20will%20be%20an%20unknown%20territory%20for%20them%20since%20they%20haven't%20played%20there%20in%20the%20past%2C%20they%20have%20plenty%20of%20options%20in%20the%20team%20to%20pick%20the%20right%20playing%20XI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Proteas)%20got%20a%20good%20side%2C%20and%20they%20are%20confident%20at%20the%20moment.%20They%20are%20playing%20well%2C%20and%20we%20watched%20the%20game%20the%20other%20day.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20nice%20surface%20in%20Delhi%2C%20and%20they%20posted%20a%20massive%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20knows%20(about%20Lucknow's%20surface)%3F%20It%20depends%20on%20what%20the%20surface%20looks%20like%20and%20how%20we%20need%20to%20play%20on%20that.%20So%2C%20we%20wait%20to%20see%20till%20we%20go%20there%20and%20figure%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20we%20have%20a%20few%20options%20that%20we%20can%20go%20in%20with.%20Marcus%20(Stoinis)%20is%20back%20with%20the%20team%20potentially.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20how%20we%20can%20fit%20them%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696837380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6pf17ic8_steve-smith-afp_625x300_09_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-had-the-wicket-to-steve-smiths-blunt-remark-on-australias-loss-against-india-in-world-cup-opener-4463432%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20rode%20on%20Virat%20Kohli's%2085%20and%20KL%20Rahul's%20unbeaten%2097-run%20knock%20to%20complete%20the%20task%20in%2041.2%20overs%2C%20having%20recovered%20from%202%2F3%20in%20the%20second%20over.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-had-the-wicket-to-steve-smiths-blunt-remark-on-australias-loss-against-india-in-world-cup-opener-4463432%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fthey-had-the-wicket-to-steve-smiths-blunt-remark-on-australias-loss-against-india-in-world-cup-opener-4463432%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22