%2C%20including%20firearms%20and%20explosives%2C%20was%20washed%20away%20by%20the%20Teesta%20river%20which%20overflowed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20glacial%20lake%20outburst%20flood%20(GLOF).%20In%20neighbouring%20West%20Bengal%2C%20a%20mortar%20shell%20washed%20by%20the%20waters%20and%20found%20by%20locals%20exploded%2C%20killing%20one%20child%20and%20injuring%20six%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-flood-another-warning-greater-disaster-risk-himalayan-states%2F%5C%22%3ESikkim%20Flood%20Was%20a%20Disaster%20Forecast%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Warnings%20Were%20Ignored%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2023%2C%20the%20Bengali%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EUttarbanga%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESangbad%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20noted%20that%20fears%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-high-court-floods-chamoli-petition-environmental-concerns%5C%22%3EUttarakhand-like%20situation%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20Sikkim%20had%20prompted%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20decision%20to%20implement%20an%20early%20warning%20system%20at%20the%20lake.%20The%20report%20had%20quoted%20Prabhakar%20Rai%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Sikkim%20State%20Disaster%20Management.%20The%20report%20also%20said%20that%20cameras%20had%20been%20installed%20at%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09122451%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-12.24.42-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09122451%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-12.24.42-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09122451%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-12.24.42-PM-300x264.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09122451%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-12.24.42-PM-1024x899.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221054%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Uttarbanga%20Sangbad%20edition%20on%20September%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%2C%20situated%20in%20Sikkim%E2%80%99s%20far%20northwestern%20region%2C%20is%20categorised%20as%20a%20glacial-moraine-dammed%20lake%20and%20is%20known%20for%20its%20rapid%20expansion%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20lakes%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Himalaya%20region%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20seismically%20active%20areas.%20In%201977%2C%20the%20lake%20covered%20an%20area%20of%2017.54%20hectares.%20Subsequent%20assessments%20of%20its%20areal%20extent%20were%20conducted%20using%20temporal%20satellite%20data%20from%201989%2C%202002%2C%20and%202008.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202015%2C%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%20identified%20South%20Lhonak%20Lake%20as%20Lake%201%20and%20estimated%20the%20area%20of%20the%20lake%20as%20136%20hectares%20and%20the%20volume%20as%2040.8%20million%20cubic%20metre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECivil%20engineer%20James%20Wilson%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20between%20September%2017%2C%202023%2C%20and%20September%2028%2C%202023%2C%20the%20surface%20area%20of%20the%20lake%20had%20increased%20by%205%20hectares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20latest%20satellite%20imagery%20on%2028.09.23%20put%20the%20area%20of%20the%20lake%20as%20167.4%20ha%20with%20a%20depth%20of%20depth%2C%20that%20would%20have%20enhanced%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20lake%20to%2083.70%20mcm%20and%20most%20probably%20would%20have%20increased%20the%20lake%20burst%20flood%20above%208000%20cumecs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLhJf7JH3Ln%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLhJf7JH3Ln%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20James%20Wilson%20(%40jamewils)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjamewils%2Fstatus%2F1710249098274595137%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20a%20significant%20leap.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Himanshu%20Thakkar%2C%20coordinator%20at%20the%20South%20Asia%20Network%20on%20Dams%2C%20Rivers%20and%20People%2C%20says%20that%20this%20was%20something%20that%20the%20monitoring%20stations%20should%20have%20caught.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CEven%20after%20the%20Chamoli%20disaster%20of%202021%2C%20the%20government%20talked%20about%20an%20early%20warning%20system.%20The%20recommendation%20for%20the%20system%20has%20been%20there%20since%202013.%20This%20is%20typical%20of%20our%20government.%20This%20is%20major%20safety%20lapse.%20The%20CWC%E2%80%99s%20monitoring%20station%20at%20Lachen%2C%2020%20km%20upstream%20from%20Chungthang%20dam%20shows%20no%20reading%20after%2010%20pm%20on%20October%203%2C%202023.%20When%20it%20was%20required%2C%20there%20was%20no%20reading.%20This%20is%20the%20status%20of%20our%20forecasting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thakkar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20CWC%20executive%20engineers%20Shashank%20Bhushan%20and%20Shailesh%20Kumar%20for%20confirmation%20of%20this.%20This%20copy%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09121518%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-10.53.54-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09121518%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-10.53.54-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09121518%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-10.53.54-AM-300x131.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09121518%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-10.53.54-AM-1024x447.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22524%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20CWC%20website%20shows%20that%20the%20last%20update%20from%20Sanklang%20(note%20that%20Thakkar%E2%80%99s%20quote%20mentions%20Lachen)%20is%20from%20October%204%2C%2012%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09134248%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-1.41.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09134248%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-1.41.10-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09134248%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-1.41.10-PM-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09134248%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-09-at-1.41.10-PM-1024x572.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-679057%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20CWC%20website%E2%80%99s%20Lachen%20page%20has%20no%20details%20on%20water%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20too%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169555X21001914%3Fvia%253Dihub%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20highlighted%20the%20increasing%20length%20of%20Lhonak%20glacial%20lake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20already%20predicted%20in%202021%20that%20this%20lake%20would%20breach%20and%20impact%20the%20dam%E2%80%A6When%20glaciers%20are%20eroding%2C%20they%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20bedrock%2C%20producing%20more%20silt.%20Whenever%20there%20is%20flash%20flooding%2C%20you%20would%20witness%20more%20silt%20and%20debris%20flowing%20downhill%2C%20aggravating%20the%20destruction%20caused%20by%20floods%20and%20landslides%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Farooq%20Azam%2C%20glaciologist%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Indore%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%202020%20publication%20by%20the%20American%20Geophysical%20Union%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20out%20of%20the%2023%20critical%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20India%2C%20a%20significant%20majority%2C%20specifically%2017%20of%20them%2C%20were%20located%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Sikkim.%20These%20lakes%20are%20classified%20as%20critical%20due%20to%20their%20potential%20to%20overflow%20as%20a%20result%20of%20melting%20glaciers%2C%20posing%20a%20risk%20of%20catastrophic%20bursting.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Kolkata-based%20Prameya%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Right%20to%20Information%20inquiry%20with%20the%20Central%20Water%20Commission%2C%20revealed%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%2016%20lakes%20identified%20as%20vulnerable%20based%20on%20a%20vulnerability%20index%2C%20the%20top%20five%20lakes%20most%20susceptible%20to%20GLOFs%20were%20all%20located%20in%20the%20Teesta%20basin%20of%20Sikkim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fdeadly-himalayan-lake-flooding-india-likely-caused-by-avalanche-2023-10-05%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%20also%20that%20Indian%20scientists%20at%20the%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20had%20said%20in%20a%202013%20report%20that%20there%20was%20a%2042%25%20chance%20of%20Lhonak%20Lake%20bursting%20its%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwaponline.com%2Fwp%2Farticle%2F22%2F4%2F641%2F74772%2FHydropower-development-along-Teesta-river-basin%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Teesta%20River%20originates%20in%20the%20northeastern%20region%20of%20Sikkim%2C%20India%2C%20at%20an%20elevation%20of%205%2C280%20metres%2C%20primarily%20from%20the%20Chombo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Jongsong%20peak%20and%20Chho%20Lhamo%20also%20contribute%20as%20sources%20of%20water.%20The%20Chungthang%20dam%20(Teesta%203%20HEP)%2C%20that%20was%20breached%2C%20is%20at%20the%20confluence%20where%20the%20Lachen%20Chu%20and%20Lachung%20Chu%20rivers%20merge%20and%20Teesta%20is%20formed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Teesta%20river%20system%20has%20the%20most%20active%20floodplain%20of%20North%20Bengal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20is%20the%20time%20to%20pause.%20There%20is%20a%20profound%20connection%20between%20rocks%2C%20trees%2C%20and%20water%3B%20this%20is%20science.%20With%20the%20increase%20in%20global%20temperatures%2C%20there%20will%20be%20extensive%20rainfall%20in%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20and%20after%20the%20Kedarnath%20disaster%2C%20the%20government%20finally%20received%20a%20report%20on%20this%20matter.%20Glacier%20melting%20is%20a%20global%20phenomenon%2C%20but%20the%20government%20should%20know%20what%20to%20do%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20environmentalist%20professor%20Moloy%20Mukhopadhyay%2C%20who%20also%20cautioned%20against%20wanton%20construction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Hydropower%20Development%20Corporation%20(NHDC)%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20there%20are%20at%20present%2047%20hydropower%20projects%20at%20various%20stages%20of%20development%20along%20the%20Teesta%20river%20in%20Sikkim%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20Among%20these%2C%20nine%20have%20already%20been%20commissioned%2C%20construction%20is%20underway%20on%2015%20dams%2C%20and%20an%20additional%2028%20are%20in%20the%20planning%20and%20development%20phases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20extensive%20Sivok-Rangpo%20rail%20project%2C%20connecting%20Rangpo%20in%20Sikkim%20to%20the%20Indian%20railway%20network%2C%20has%20raised%20environmental%20concerns.%20Geologists%20caution%20the%20possibility%20of%20compromising%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20mountains%2C%20elevating%20the%20potential%20for%20landslides%20and%20natural%20disasters.%20The%20region%20also%20witnesses%20a%20constant%20influx%20of%20thousands%20of%20tourist%20vehicles%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CAs%20many%20as%2014%20tunnels%20are%20being%20excavated%20for%20the%20Sevoke-Rangpo%20railway%20line%20on%20this%20delicate%20mountain%20terrain.%20Regardless%20of%20the%20stability%20of%20the%20project%2C%20continuous%20tunnelling%20is%20causing%20seismic%20activity%2C%20raising%20the%20risk%20of%20landslides%20and%20glacier%20ruptures%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Animesh%20Basu%2C%20an%20environmentalist%20from%20the%20Himalayan%20Nature%20and%20Adventure%20Foundation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBasu%20called%20the%20situation%20dire%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20one%20side%20stands%20Sikkim%E2%80%99s%20vital%20lifeline%2C%20the%20Teesta%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20side%20are%20Siliguri%20and%20Jalpaiguri%3B%20if%20a%20catastrophe%20occurs%2C%20and%20the%20Teesta%20and%20Mahananda%20rivers%20converge%2C%20the%20very%20existence%20of%20settlements%20in%20this%20area%20would%20be%20in%20jeopardy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGautam%20Sarkar%2C%20a%20senior%20editor%20at%20%3Cem%3EUttarbanga%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESangbad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20concludes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Himalayas%20are%20still%20evolving%20mountains%2C%20characterised%20by%20their%20composition%20of%20alluvial%20soil%2C%20rendering%20them%20naturally%20fragile.%20The%20disaster%20cannot%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20Sevoke-Rangpo%20railway%20line.%20Nevertheless%2C%20this%20railway%20line%20does%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20potential%20for%20future%20disasters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696834842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09130011%2FUntitled-design-10.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-disaster-flood-warning%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Multiple%20studies%2C%20reports%20and%20RTI%20responses%20have%20it%20that%20it%20was%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20lake%20was%20vulnerable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-disaster-flood-warning%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajveer's%20Dono%20struggles%20to%20cross%20Rs%201%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696834455000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104275427%2Cimgsize-41812.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdono-box-office-collection-day-3-rajveer-deols-debut-film-struggles-to-cross-rs-1-crore%2Farticleshow%2F104275427.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104275427.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThis%20romantic%20drama%20is%20directed%20by%20deb