i%3EKal%20Ho%20Naa%20Ho%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20directed%20by%20Nikhil%20Advani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20caption%2C%20Mahira%20Khan%20mentioned%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9Claid%20out%20a%20few%20requests%E2%80%9D%20to%20her%20friends%20and%20cousins%20but%20they%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20of%20no%20use.%20Mahira%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20a%20good.%20What%20a%20Best.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20told%20my%20friends%20about%20the%20wedding%E2%80%A6%20I%20also%20laid%20out%20a%20few%20%E2%80%98requests'.%20This%20is%20how%20they%20went%3A%20Me%20-%20Guys%20please%20I'm%20too%20old%20for%20dances%2C%20can%20we%20not%20have%20dances%3F%20Friends%20-%20No.%20we%20have%20to.%20M%20-%20Ok%20just%20one%3F%20F%20-%20Hell%20No.%20M%20-%20Ok%20please%20no%20dholkis%20before%20Bhurban.%20We%20should%20all%20just%20chill.%20F%20-%20talk%20to%20the%20%5Bhand%20emoji%5D%20As%20time%20came%20close%20and%20they%20all%20were%20over%20every%20day...I%20realised%20they%20just%20wanted%20to%20celebrate%20me%20and%20us.%20My%20childhood%20friends%2C%20work%20friends%2C%20my%20cousins%E2%80%A6%20had%20seen%20it%20all%20with%20me%20-%20held%20me%20when%20I%20was%20down%20and%20clapped%20when%20I%20succeeded.%20I%20had%20done%20the%20same%20with%20them.%20To%20these%20insanely%20amazing%20humans%2C%20I%20call%20family.%20I%20love%20you%20all%20so%20freaking%20much.%20Alhumdulillah.%20MashAllah.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fswirlster.ndtv.com%2Fstyle%2Ftradition-was-beautifully-rooted-in-mahira-khans-pre-wedding-outfits-4455759%23ndtv_related%5C%22%3EMahira%20Khan%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20wrote%20a%20sweet%20note%20for%20her%20%E2%80%9Cbestest%20friend%20in%20the%20whole%20world.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CPS%20My%20bestest%20friend%20in%20the%20whole%20world%20surprised%20me%20at%20the%20Mehndi%20and%20I%20still%20can't%20believe%20she%20made%20it.%20It's%20her%20birthday%20today%20-%20I%20love%20you%20my%20insia%20lotia.%20Always%20and%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C