bout%20the%20'assassination%20'%20of%20Sikh%20religious%20leader%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20Canada%20have%20emerged%20from%20within%20the%20CCP.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20'assassination'%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20CCP%20agents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%2018%20June%202023%2C%20Hardeep%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20India%2C%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20of%20the%20Guru%20Nanak%20Sikh%20Gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20independent%20blogger%20attributed%20her%20allegations%20to%20Chinese%20writer%20and%20YouTuber%20Lao%20Deng%2C%20who%20according%20to%20her%2C%20lives%20in%20Canada%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLao%20stated%20that%20in%20early%20June%20this%20year%20as%20part%20of%20their%20disruption%20initiative%20'Ignition%20Plan'%2C%20the%20CCP%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%20sent%20a%20high-ranking%20official%20to%20Seattle%2C%20USA.%20A%20secret%20meeting%20was%20held%20there...The%20objective%20was%20to%20sabotage%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20West%2C%26quot%3B%20Zeng%20claims%20in%20the%20video%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agents%20were%20tasked%20with%20assassinating%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20Sikh%20leader%20in%20Canada.%20Following%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20CCP%20agents%20meticulously%20executed%20the%20killing%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20their%20modus%20operandi%2C%20the%20independent%20blogger%20alleges%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20June%2018th%2C%20the%20agents%20armed%20with%20silenced%20guns%20tracked%20Nijjar.%20When%20the%20deed%20was%20done%2C%20they%20destroyed%20the%20dash%20camera%20in%20Nijjar's%20Car%20to%20erase%20any%20evidence.%20After%20the%20crime%2C%20the%20agents%20fled%2C%20they%20burned%20their%20weapons%20and%20disguises%20to%20destroy%20all%20traces.%20The%20next%20day%20they%20left%20Canada%20in%20Airplanes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20killers%20even%20purposely%20learned%20Indian-accent%20English.%20%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20they%20purposely%20spoke%20in%20India%20accent%20English...In%20fact%2C%20these%20actions%20were%20part%20of%20the%20scheme%20by%20CCP%20secret%20agent%20to%20frame%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zeng.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20claimed%20that%20Lao%20revealed%20that%20the%20CCP's%20'ignition%20plan'%20was%20devised%20this%20year%20after%20the%20CCP's%20two%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20response%20to%20Jennifer%20Zeng's%20allegations%2C%20posted%20in%20the%20video%20on%20Sunday%20afternonn%20(US%20time)%20from%20either%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diplomatic%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20soured%20after%20the%20Canadian%20government%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%20accusing%20India%20of%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%2C%20India%20swiftly%20retaliated%20by%20issuing%20a%20statement%20that%20denied%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20issue%20and%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat.%20India%20has%20outrightly%20rejected%20the%20claims%2C%20calling%20it%20'absurd'%20and%20'motivated'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20escalating%20tensions%2C%20India%20has%20called%20for%20parity%20in%20the%20number%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinistry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20earlier%20this%20month%20said%20that%20Canadian%20diplomatic%20presence%20is%20much%20higher%20in%20India%20and%20they%20assume%20%26quot%3Bthere%20would%20be%20reduction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20discussions%20on%20parity%2C%20given%20the%20much%20higher%20presence%20of%20diplomats%20or%20diplomatic%20presence%20here%20and%20their%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20matters%2C%20we%20have%20sought%20parity%20in%20our%20respective%20diplomatic%20presence.%20Discussions%20are%20ongoing%20to%20achieve%20this.%20Given%20that%20Canadian%20diplomatic%20presence%20is%20higher%2C%20we%20would%20assume%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20reduction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696832100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fu7o4bfig_hardeep-singh-nijjar-_625x300_24_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-behind-khalistani-terrorist-hardeep-singh-nijjars-killing-in-canada-blogger-says-this-4462787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alleging%20that%20agents%20of%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20were%20involved%20in%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20an%20independent%20blogger%2C%20Jennifer%20Zeng%2C%20has%20said%20China's%20%26quot%3Bpurpose%20was%20to%20frame%20India%20creating%20discord%20between%20India%20and%20the%20West%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-behind-khalistani-terrorist-hardeep-singh-nijjars-killing-in-canada-blogger-says-this-4462787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-behind-khalistani-terrorist-hardeep-singh-nijjars-killing-in-canada-blogger-says-this-4462787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-behind-khalistani-terrorist-hardeep-singh-nijjars-killing-in-canada-blogger-says-this-4462787%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gauahar%20Khan's%20befitting%20answer%20to%20a%20netizen%20who%20called%20her%20'Hamas%20Supporter'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696832028000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104275727%2Cimgsize-728438.cms%22%2C%22originID%2