html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eyet%20to%20be%20arrested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20do%20Canadian%20government%20statistics%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20Indians%20and%20Hindus%3F%20The%20police-reported%20hate%20crimes%20do%20not%20have%20a%20separate%20victim%2Fperpetrator%20category%20for%20Indians%2C%20Hindus%20or%20Sikhs%2C%20who%20are%20instead%20subsumed%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98South%20Asian%E2%80%99%20ethnicity%20and%20%E2%80%9Cother%20religion%E2%80%9D%20(not%20Jewish%2C%20Muslim%20or%20Catholic)%20categories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20statistics%20(which%20are%20available%20only%20until%202021)%20will%20give%20some%2C%20if%20not%20a%20definitive%2C%20indication%20of%20the%20threats%20that%20Indians%2FHindus%20face.%20After%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20like%20in%20many%20other%20countries%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww150.statcan.gc.ca%2Fn1%2Fdaily-quotidien%2F230322%2Ft001a-eng.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esubstantial%20increase%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20hate%20crimes%20in%20terms%20of%20ethnicity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fhate-speech-what-it-is-and-why-it-matters%5C%22%3EHate%20Speech%3A%20What%20It%20Is%20and%20Why%20It%20Matters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20has%20been%20mainly%20accounted%20for%20by%20the%20nearly%20five-time%20increase%20in%20crimes%20faced%20by%20East%2FSoutheast%20Asians.%20Hate%20crimes%20against%20South%20Asians%20(not%20just%20Indians)%20doubled%20in%202021%20compared%20to%202019%2C%20but%20still%20constituted%20only%209.5%25%20of%20all%20ethnicity-motivated%20hate%20crimes%20in%20Canada%2C%20representing%20an%20increase%20from%207.6%25%20in%202017%20(South%20Asians%20make%20up%207%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20population).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBlacks%20faced%20the%20highest%20percentage%20of%20ethnicity-motivated%20hate%20crimes%20at%2037%25%2C%20when%20their%20population%20share%20is%20only%204%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20religion%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20real%20increase%20in%20total%20hate%20crimes%20during%202017-2021.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cother%20religion%E2%80%9D%20(Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20etc.)%20category%20saw%20around%207%25%20of%20the%20religious%20hate%20crimes%20in%202021%2C%20roughly%20the%20same%20percent%20as%20their%20population.%20Here%2C%20Jews%20faced%20a%20staggering%2055%25%20of%20hate%20crimes%2C%20despite%20being%20only%201%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20population%20(in%202017%2C%20Muslims%20faced%2041%25%20of%20the%20crimes%20with%20a%20population%20of%20only%204%25).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilar%20kinds%20of%20statistics%20emerge%20elsewhere.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1043735%2Fwhat-fbi-data-about-anti-hindu-hate-crimes-in-the-us-reveals-about-fears-of-hinduphobia%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20anti-African%20American%20hate%20was%20the%20highest%20and%20of%20which%20there%20were%20200%20times%20more%20incidents%20than%20of%20anti-Hindu%20hate.%20Even%20Sikhs%20were%20%E2%80%9C128%20times%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emore%20likely%20to%20be%20victims%20of%20hate%20crimes%20than%20Hindus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Anti-Hindu%20hate%2C%20with%2010%20cases%2C%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20coming%20in%20at%2034th%20out%20of%2035%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-63157965%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEngland%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2040%25%20of%20religious%20hate%20crimes%20targeted%20Muslims%2C%20despite%20their%20being%20only%206.5%25%20of%20the%20population%20(in%20England%20and%20Wales)%2C%20while%20Jews%2C%20at%200.5%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20were%20the%20second-most%20commonly%20targeted!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.australianjewishnews.com%2Fhate-in-australia-the-statistics%2F%5C%22%3EAnd%20in%20Australia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jews%20were%20the%20most%20targeted%20despite%20again%20being%20a%20minuscule%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Canada%2C%20hate%20crimes%20constituted%200.1%25%20of%20two%20million%20police-reported%20crimes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww150.statcan.gc.ca%2Fn1%2Fpub%2F85-002-x%2F2022001%2Farticle%2F00005-eng.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%2056%25%20of%20the%20hate%20crimes%20in%202021%20were%20non-violent%20crimes%20like%20general%20mischief%2C%20mischief%20in%20relation%20to%20a%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20and%20public%20incitement%20of%20hatred.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmongst%20South%20Asian%20victims%20(2011-2020)%2C%201%25%20faced%20a%20major%20physical%20injury.%20Because%20of%20the%20difficulty%20of%20identifying%20a%20perpetrator%2C%20non-violent%20hate%20crimes%20are%20cleared%20at%20a%20much%20lower%20rate%20than%20violent%20hate%20crimes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjustin-trudeau-india-canada-china%5C%22%3ECanada-India%20Tensions%20Complicate%20Western%20Efforts%20to%20Rein%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Indians%20and%20Hindus%20can%20legitimately%20ask%20the%20Canadian%20state%20for%20the%20better%20enforcement%20of%20its%20laws%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hate%20incidents%2C%20what%20has%20obfuscated%20reality%20since%20the%20rapid%20rise%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20is%20the%20drastically%20inflated%2C%20propagandist-media-driven%20sense%20of%20victimhood%20amongst%20Hindus%2C%20including%20in%20the%20West.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20becomes%20virulently%20pushed%20by%20diaspora%20Hindu%20nationalist%20groups%20to%20not%20just%20describe%20acts%20of%20genuine%20hate%20against%20Hindus%2C%20but%20to%20deflect%20attempts%20of%20caste%20critique%20(betraying%20their%20Brahminical%2Fupper-caste%20nature)%20or%20the%20criticism%20of%20Hindutva%20political%20ideology%20%E2%80%93%20representing%20the%20fusing%20of%20Hindu%20supremacism%20with%20the%20state%20(which%20has%20seen%20hate%20speech%20by%20the%20highest%20government%20functionaries%20and%20produced%20grievous%20violence%20against%20minorities%20in%20India).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20manifests%20in%20the%20organised%20castigation%20of%20the%20recognition%20of%20caste-based%20discrimination%20in%20schools%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Fnews-and-politics%2F2023%2F09%2Fcalifornia-anti-caste-discrimination-bill-hindu-nationalism-hindutva.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estate%20laws%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20North%20America.%20Bizarrely%2C%20the%20argument%20is%20that%20officially%20acknowledging%20caste%20discrimination%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F09%2F30%2Fworld%2Fcanada%2Fmodi-canada-hindu-nationalism.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cdemonises%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Hinduism.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20stark%20example%20of%20how%20the%20legitimate%20Hindu%20demand%20for%20protection%20against%20hate%20is%20conflated%20with%20an%20imagined%20Hinduphobia%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20response%20to%20Toronto-based%20Indian%20filmmaker%20Leena%20Manimekalai%2C%20who%20had%20depicted%20Goddess%20Kali%20as%20smoking%20and%20holding%20an%20LGBT%20flag%20in%20her%20film%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fayodhya-priest-threatens-to-behead-filmmaker-leena-manimekalai%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esubjected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20a%20torrent%20of%20hate%20messages%20and%20death%2Frape%20threats.%20FIRs%20were%20filed%20in%20multiple%20Indian%20states%20until%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-protects-filmmaker-leena-manimekalai-from-arrest-over-kaali-poster-101674201386639.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESupreme%20Court%20of%20India%20protected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20her%20from%20arrests.%20Ironically%2C%20Manimekalai%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecelebrating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Kali%20by%20drawing%20upon%20folk%20imaginations%20of%20an%20inclusive%20goddess%20who%20drinks%2C%20eats%20and%20smokes%20with%20the%20most%20marginalized%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECrucially%2C%20Canadian%20institutions%2Funiversities%20hosting%20the%20film%20distanced%20from%20it%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Fstyle%2Farticle%2Fkaali-hindu-goddess-leena-manimekalai%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eissued%20apologies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20thus%20failing%20to%20safeguard%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Canadian%20Charter%20of%20Rights%20and%20Freedoms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F9HA0Tm92s3w%3Fsi%3DfO32L2NEEGlcQGYF%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArya%2C%20Trudeau%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20now%20rightly%20seeking%20action%20against%20Khalistani%20hate%20speech%2C%20had%20then%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAryaCanada%2Fstatus%2F1544413469059186688%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etermed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Manimekalai%E2%80%99s%20work%20as%20%