potlight%20After%20Hamas%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas's%20surprise%20assault%20on%20Israel%20Saturday%20and%20Israel's%20retaliation%20have%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C100%20people%20and%20focused%20attention%20on%20the%20Iran-backed%20Islamist%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20Iran%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20able%20to%20spend%20a%20single%20dollar%20of%20the%20%246%20billion%20in%20funds%20that%20were%20unfrozen%20in%20a%20US-Iran%20prisoner%20swap%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20also%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bnot%20yet%20seen%20evidence%20that%20Iran%20directed%20or%20was%20behind%20this%20particular%20attack%2C%20but%20there's%20certainly%20a%20long%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20iran%20prisoner%20swap%20deal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20details%20were%20made%20public%20of%20a%20complicated%20agreement%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20approved.%20Five%20US%20citizens%20detained%20by%20Tehran%20were%20allowed%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20transfer%20of%20%246%20billion%20in%20Iranian%20funds%20that%20had%20been%20frozen%20in%20South%20Korea.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20five%20Iranians%20held%20in%20the%20United%20States%20were%20allowed%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20%246%20Billion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%246%20billion%20was%20Iranian%20money%20that%20had%20been%20frozen%20in%20South%20Korean%20banks.%20After%20Washington%2C%20under%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20placed%20a%20total%20ban%20on%20Iran's%20oil%20exports%20and%20sanctions%20on%20its%20banking%20sector%20in%202019%2C%20these%20Iranian%20oil%20revenues%20were%20blocked%20in%20Seoul.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20is%20the%20%246%20billion%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20funds%20were%20not%20dispersed%20to%20Iran.%20Qatar's%20central%20bank%20is%20overseeing%20the%20funds%2C%20which%20are%20still%20in%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20facts%20are%20these%20-%20no%20US%20taxpayer%20dollars%20were%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20told%20CNN's%20%26quot%3BState%20of%20the%20Union%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BThese%20were%20Iranian%20resources%20that%20Iran%20had%20accumulated%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20its%20oil%20that%20were%20stuck%20in%20a%20bank%20in%20South%20Korea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20Iran%20prisoner%20deal%2C%20the%20money%20can%20only%20be%20used%20for%20humanitarian-related%20purposes%2C%20including%20purchasing%20food%20or%20other%20goods%20outside%20Iran%20for%20import%2C%20US%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Treasury's%20undersecretary%20for%20terrorism%20and%20finance%2C%20Brian%20Nelson%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20the%20money%20held%20in%20restricted%20accounts%20in%20Doha%20as%20part%20of%20the%20arrangement%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20five%20Americans%20in%20September%20remains%20in%20Doha.%20Not%20a%20penny%20has%20been%20spent.%20These%20restricted%20funds%20cannot%20go%20to%20Iran%20-%20it%20can%20only%20be%20used%20for%20future%20humanitarian-related%20purposes.%20Any%20suggestion%20to%20the%20contrary%20is%20false%20and%20misleading.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20due%20diligence%20requirements%20related%20to%20the%20swap%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20take%20many%20months%20for%20Iran%20to%20spend%20down%20this%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20as%20we've%20said%20many%20times%2C%20it%20can%20only%20be%20used%20to%20purchase%20food%2C%20medicine%2C%20medical%20devices%2C%20and%20agricultural%20products%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20critics%20of%20the%20deal%20saying%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Republicans%20vying%20to%20be%20the%20party's%202024%20presidential%20nominee%20tried%20to%20link%20Biden's%20Iran%20deal%20to%20the%20attacks%2C%20with%20some%20alleging%2C%20incorrectly%2C%20that%20he%20or%20US%20taxpayers%20funded%20the%20attacks%20on%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAllowing%20Iran%20access%20to%20those%20funds%20under%20any%20circumstances%20improves%20its%20budget%20situation%2C%20freeing%20up%20money%20that%20would%20be%20used%20to%20use%20elsewhere%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20the%20former%20South%20Carolina%20governor%20and%202024%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20be%20honest%20with%20the%20American%20people%20and%20understand%20that%20Hamas%20knows%2C%20and%20Iran%20knows%20they're%20moving%20money%20around%20as%20we%20speak%2C%20because%20they%20know%20%246%20billion%20is%20going%20to%20be%20released.%20That's%20the%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696825680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fpu05jcao_israel_625x300_08_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-gaza-hamas-explained-why-6-billion-us-iran-deal-is-in-spotlight-after-hamas-attack-4462985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas's%20surprise%20assault%20on%20Israel%20Saturday%20and%20Israel's%20retaliation%20have%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C100%20people%20and%20focused%20attention%20on%20the%20Iran-backed%20Islamist%20group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-war-gaza-hamas-explained-why-6-billion-us-iran-deal-is-in-spotlight-after-hamas-attack-4462985%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2