.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-lifts-tsunami-advisory-for-coastal-areas%2Famp_articleshow%2F104272988.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Extent%20of%20Falsehoods%20Astounding'%3A%20Farmers%20Launch%20Nationwide%20Protest%20Against%20Allegations%20in%20NewsClick%20FIR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F06123423%2FFarmers2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Samkyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20%E2%80%93%20the%20umbrella%20body%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20that%20was%20formed%20during%20the%20agitation%20against%20the%20contentious%20and%20now%20repealed%20farm%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20has%20announced%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20for%20what%20it%20has%20called%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Crenewed%20attack%E2%80%9D%20on%20farmers%2C%20by%20mentioning%20the%20protests%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fdelhi-police-terror-fir-against-newsclick-names-chinese-firms-xiaomi-vivo-puts-lawyers-in-crosshairs%5C%22%3EFIR%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSKM%20categorically%20rejects%20all%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%2C%20the%20same%20being%20false%20and%20motivated%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20against%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20editor-in-chief%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20two%20others%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20accused%20persons%20have%20also%20conspired%20to%20disrupt%20supplies%20and%20services%20essential%20to%20the%20life%20of%20community%20in%20India%20and%20abet%20damage%20and%20destruction%20of%20property%20by%20protraction%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20through%20such%20illegal%20foreign%20funding%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%20of%20above%20nexus%20was%20to%20promote%E2%80%A6%20funding%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20causing%20huge%20loss%20of%20several%20hundred%20crores%20to%20Indian%20economy%20and%20create%20internal%20law%20and%20order%20problems%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20has%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshocked%E2%80%9D%20to%20learn%20of%20these%20allegations%2C%20and%20farmers%20neither%20destroyed%20any%20properties%20nor%20disrupted%20any%20supply%20lines.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20violently%20stopping%20the%20farmers%20from%20exercising%20their%20democratic%20right%20of%20reaching%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20through%20barbed%20wire%20fencing%2C%20water%20cannons%2C%20lathi%20charge%20and%20digging%20up%20roads%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Union%20Govt.%20that%20caused%20great%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20farmers%20%E2%80%A6It%20is%20the%20Govt.%20that%20conspired%20with%20crony%20capitalists%20to%20grab%20and%20capture%20food%20production%20and%20supply%20chains%2C%20destroying%20food%20security%20of%20the%20people%20and%20economy%20of%20the%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20surprising%2C%20the%20statement%20says%2C%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20that%20comes%20under%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20is%20making%20false%20allegations%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthough%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20falsehoods%20is%20astounding%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESKM%20has%20also%20expressed%20its%20solidarity%20with%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20other%20independent%20media%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSKM%20announces%20nationwide%20mass%20protests%20against%20this%20BJP-led%20Union%20Govt%20for%20its%20renewed%20attack%20on%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20through%20the%20Newsclick%20FIR.%20Every%20state%20capital%2C%20district%20head%20quarter%2C%20tehsil%20head%20quarter%20shall%20see%20mass%20protest%20gatherings%20demanding%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20false%20and%20scurrilous%20allegations%20made%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20in%20the%20Newsclick%20FIR%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20SKM%E2%80%99s%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Samyukt%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20is%20shocked%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20scurrilous%20and%20malafide%20allegations%20made%20against%20the%20historic%20SKM-led%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20at%20Delhi%2C%20in%20the%20FIR%20lodged%20by%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20media%20house%20Newsclick%20and%20several%20journalists.%20SKM%20categorically%20rejects%20all%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%2C%20the%20same%20being%20false%20and%20motivated%2C%20and%20unequivocally%20places%20on%20record%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1)%20SKM%20rejects%20the%20patently%20false%20and%20mischievous%20allegations%20in%20the%20FIR%20that%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20aimed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdisrupt%20supplies%20and%20services%20essential%20to%20the%20life%20of%20the%20community%20in%20India%2C%20abet%20damage%20and%20destruction%20of%20property%2C%20cause%20huge%20loss%20to%20the%20Indian%20economy%20and%20create%20internal%20law%20and%20order%20problems%2C%20through%20illegal%20foreign%20funding%E2%80%9D.%20Farmers%2C%20the%20annadatas%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20participated%20in%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20led%20by%20the%20SKM%20against%20the%20anti-farmer%20and%20pro-corporate%20laws%20and%20policies%20of%20the%20BJP%20Govt.%20No%20supply%20was%20disrupted%20by%20farmers.%20No%20property%20was%20damaged%20by%20farmers.%20No%20loss%20to%20the%20economy%20was%20caused%20by%20farmers.%20No%20law%20and%20order%20problem%20was%20created%20by%20farmers.%20By%20violently%20stopping%20the%20farmers%20from%20exercising%20their%20democratic%20right%20of%20reaching%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20through%20barbed%20wire%20fencing%2C%20water%20cannons%2C%20lathi%20charge%20and%20digging%20up%20roads%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Union%20Govt.%20that%20caused%20great%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20the%20farmers.%20Farmers%20had%20to%20sit%20in%20protest%20for%2013%20long%20months%2C%20under%20the%20blazing%20summer%20sun%2C%20torrential%20rains%20and%20freezing%20winter%20cold.%20It%20is%20the%20Union%20Govt.%20and%20BJP-RSS%20combine%20that%20created%20law%20and%20order%20problems%20by%20mowing%20down%20farmers%20at%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20under%20running%20vehicles%2C%20killing%20four%20farmers%20and%20one%20journalist.%20The%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%20and%20his%20son%20were%20behind%20this%20attack.%20Till%20now%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20not%20removed%20the%20delinquent%20Minister%20and%20ensured%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20culprits.%20735%20farmers%20including%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20farmers%20had%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20lives%20to%20counter%20the%20repression%20by%20the%20Modi%20Government.%20It%20is%20the%20Govt.%20that%20destroyed%20public%20property.%20It%20is%20the%20Govt.%20that%20conspired%20with%20crony%20capitalists%20to%20grab%20and%20capture%20food%20production%20and%20supply%20chains%2C%20destroying%20food%20security%20of%20the%20people%20and%20economy%20of%20the%20nation.%20Funds%20from%20China%20have%20been%20received%20by%20PM%20Modi%20in%20PM%20Cares%20Fund%20and%20by%20Gautam%20Adani%20in%20his%20business.%20The%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20succeeded%2C%20overcoming%20enormous%20hardship%20and%20with%20great%20sacrifice%20of%20the%20farmers.%20To%20belittle%20such%20a%20sacrifice%20by%20alleging%20that%20the%20movement%20was%20foreign%20funded%20and%20led%20to%20acts%20of%20terrorism%2C%20betrays%20the%20arrogance%2C%20ignorance%20and%20anti-people%20mindset%20of%20the%20Union%20Govt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2)%20SKM%20strongly%20denounces%20the%20attempt%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20Govt.%20to%20underplay%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20immensely%20patriotic%20and%20historic%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20which%20was%20against%20this%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20hand%20over%20Indian%20farming%20to%20big%20corporates%20including%20foreign%20exploiters.%20It%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20the%203%20black%20farm%20laws%20tried%20to%20establish%20legal%20control%20of%20corporates%20over%20the%20cropping%20pattern%20through%20contract%20farming%2C%20over%20mandis%2C%20food%20processing%20and%20food%20distribution%20through%20the%20Mandi%20Act%20and%20modifications%20in%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%2C%20and%20to%20do%20away%20with%20Govt.%20procurement%2C%20price%20support%20and%20PDS%20Ration%20security.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20laws%20were%20anti-people%20and%20unpatriotic%20while%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20was%20a%20spontenous%20expression%20of%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20nationalism.%20This%20FIR%20is%20a%20crafty%20and%20nefarious%20plan%20to%20portray%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20as%20funded%20by%20some%20extraneous%20sources%2C%20a%20ploy%20firmly%20rejected%20by%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20Movement%2C%20and%20before%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP-RSS%20Govt%20had%20been%20forced%20to%20surrender%20its%20fabricated%20claims.%20Indian%20farming%20not%20only%20provides%20for%20food%20security%20to%20142%20crore%20people%2C%20it%20provides%20subsistence%20to%2090%20crore%20rural%20folk%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20which%20was%20seen%20by%20all%20during%20the%20Corona%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3)%20Since%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20is%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Union%20Govt.%20and%20commanded%20by%20known%20anti-farmer%20leaders%20like%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20it%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20false%20allegations%20have%20been%20made%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%2C%20though%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20falsehoods%20is%20astounding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4)%20SKM%20understands%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20Govt.%2C%20still%20smarting%20from%20the%20humiliation%20of%20having%20to%20roll%20back%20the%203%20black%20farm%20laws%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20determined%2C%20democratic%20and%20peaceful%20agitation%20of%20lakhs%20of%20farmers%20at%20the%20borders%20of%20Delhi%20and%20throughout%20the%20country%20from%20November%202020%20to%20December%202021%2C%20will%20continuously%20try%20to%20take%20revenge%20against%20farmers%20by%20tainting%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20and%20building%20an%20anti-farmer%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20SKM%2C%20through%20its%20constituent%20organisations%2C%20has%20already%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20independent%20media%20houses%20like%20Newsclick%20and%20with%20scores%20of%20journalists%20who%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20write%20and%20publish%20the%20truth%20about%20this%20anti-people%20BJP-led%20Union%20Govt.%20and%20denounced%20the%20nefarious%20attempts%20of%20the%20Govt.%20to%20muzzle%20and%20choke%20their%20voices%20through%20false%20cases%20and%20arrests%20by%20illegal%20misuse%20of%20state%20machinery%20and%20power%2C%20the%20SKM%20once%20again%20expresses%20solidarity%20with%20Newsclick%20and%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20independent%20media%20and%20reiterates%20that%20it%20shall%20support%20all%20classes%20and%20sections%20of%20citizens%20in%20ensuring%20that%20their%20rights%20are%20not%20trampled%20upon%20by%20this%20Govt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESKM%20announces%20nationwide%20mass%20protests%20against%20this%20BJP-led%20Union%20Govt%20for%20its%20renewed%20attack%20on%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20through%20the%20Newsclick%20FIR.%20Every%20state%20capital%2C%20district%20head%20quarter%2C%20tehsil%20head%20quarter%20shall%20see%20mass%20protest%20gatherings%20demanding%20immediate%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20false%20and%20scurrilous%20allegations%20made%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%20in%20the%20Newsclick%20FIR.%20Deputations%20shall%20be%20submitted%20by%20delegations%20of%20the%20SKM%20leaders%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20Prime%20Minster%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%2C%20Union%20Agriculture%20Minister%20and%20Commissioner%20of%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20immediately%20withdraw%20all%20allegations%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%2C%20failing%20which%20sit-in%20protests%20and%20demonstrations%20shall%20be%20held%20at%20the%20offices%20of%20all%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696825566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F06123423%2FFarmers2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fextent-of-falsehoods-astounding-farmers-group-to-protest-against-allegations-in-newsclick-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSKM%20categorically%20rejects%20all%20allegations%20made%20in%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Movement%2C%20the%20same%20being%20false%20and%20motivated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fextent-of-falsehoods-astounding-farmers-group-to-protest-against-allegations-in-newsclick-fir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20would%20need%20a%20massive%20ground%20assault%20with%20tanks%20to%20rescue%20hostages%20in%20Gaza%20that%20would%20be%20a%20'bloody%20mess'%20and%20devastate%20civilian%20areas%2C%20retired%204-star%20general%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ret.%20Gen.%20Barry%20McCaffrey%20speaks%20at%20a%20conference%20in%202014%2C%20next%20to%20an%20image%20of%20Palestinians%20taking%20a%20hostage%20from%20Israel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652379786561dd877e745197%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2