%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Tourists%20Stranded%20at%20Bethlehem%20to%20Be%20Brought%20Back%20Through%20Egypt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F09084234%2FScreenshot-2023-10-09-at-8.41.54-AM_cleanup.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Around%20200%20Indian%20pilgrims%20and%20tourists%20in%20Bethlehem%20who%20were%20stranded%20due%20to%20the%20fighting%20in%20the%20region%20are%20being%20brought%20back%20via%20Egypt.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20further%20reported%20incidents%20involving%20Indian%20nationals%20entangled%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20massive%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%20600%20Israelis%2C%20including%20soldiers%2C%20are%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20unprecedented%20attack%20by%20the%20militant%20group%20at%20multiple%20locations%2C%20from%20the%20Gaza%20strip.%20In%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20counterattack%2C%20at%20least%20370%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20as%20per%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20around%20200%20Indian%20nationals%20were%20reported%20to%20have%20been%20stranded%20in%20the%20Bethlehem%20region%2C%20which%20is%20a%20hub%20for%20Christian%20pilgrims%20and%20tourists.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Meghalaya%20chief%20minister%20Conrad%20Sangma%20had%20said%20that%20around%2027%20pilgrims%20were%20in%20that%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20has%20been%20able%20to%20facilitate%20their%20return%20through%20the%20road%20route%20by%20the%20Egyptian%20border%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPTI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20there%20are%20around%2018%2C000%20Indian%20nationals%20studying%20and%20working%20in%20Israel%2C%20but%20there%2C%20