20manifested%20here.%20Germany%20has%20also%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2019%2F12%2F17%2Fgolwalkars-dream-come-true-why-citizenship-law-has-hindu-rashtra-written-all-over-it%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eshown%20how%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20well-nigh%20impossible%20it%20is%20for%20Races%20and%20cultures%2C%20having%20differences%20going%20to%20the%20root%2C%20to%20be%20assimilated%20into%20one%20united%20whole%2C%20a%20good%20lesson%20for%20us%20in%20Hindustan%20to%20learn%20and%20profit%20by.%E2%80%9D%20In%20response%20to%20this%2C%20Hindutva%20nationalist%20panelists%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20context%20and%20cherry%20picking%20does%20not%20reflect%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20person%20or%20the%20organisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20counter%20this%2C%20a%20panelist%20quoted%20his%20interview%20with%20Khushwant%20Singh%2C%20the%20editor%20of%20%E2%80%98Illustrated%20Weekly%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20in%201972%2C%20according%20to%20which%20Golwalkar%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20to%20historical%20factors%2C%20Muslims%20have%20divided%20loyalties.%20But%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D289256920559445%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Efor%20this%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20both%20are%20responsible.%E2%80%9D%20Further%20one%20may%20add%20that%20the%20present%20%3Cem%3Esarsanghchalak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief)%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20in%20his%20Vigyan%20Bhavan%20speeches%20in%202018%2C%20talked%20in%20more%20conciliatory%20terms%20and%20later%20also%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Hindu%20and%20Muslims%20have%20the%20same%20DNA.%20He%20also%20took%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Falwar-mob-lynching-case-member-naval-kishore-sharma-arrested-1816287-2021-06-18%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethose%20indulging%20in%20lynching%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20against%20Hindutva%E2%80%A6%20Though%20at%20times%2C%20some%20false%20cases%20of%20lynching%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20people%E2%80%A6Don%E2%80%99t%20get%20trapped%20in%20the%20cycle%20of%20fear%20that%20Islam%20is%20in%20danger%20in%20India%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20a%20change%20in%20language%20from%20the%201939%20book%20to%20the%201972%20interview%20and%20now%20that%20of%20the%20present%20RSS%20chief.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20deeds%20resulting%20from%20the%20vast%20RSS%20combine%2C%20which%20Golwalkar%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20building%20in%3F%20What%20is%20taught%20in%20RSS%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshakhas%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(local%20RSS%20branches)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Sarswati%20%3Cem%3EVidyalayas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(RSS-run%20schools)%2C%20what%20is%20propagated%20through%20the%20right-wing%20IT%20cell%20and%20the%20social%20media%20controlled%20by%20this%20hydra%20headed%20organisation%3F%20It%20is%20pure%20%E2%80%98hate%20other%E2%80%99%20ideology%20which%20dominates%20its%20teachings.%20The%20intent%20of%20the%20organisation%20does%20not%20lie%20in%20the%20mere%20changing%20articulation%20but%20on%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20social%20fabric%2C%20on%20the%20hapless%20Muslim%20minority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20way%20what%20Golwalkar%20said%20in%201937%20is%20the%20ground%20reality%20today.%20One%20after%20the%20other%2C%20incidents%20tell%20the%20religious%20minorities%20that%20their%20place%20in%20this%20system%20is%20secondary%2C%20they%20can%20live%20here%20only%20as%20a%20marginalised%20community%20without%20asking%20for%20citizens%20rights.%20When%20lynchings%20were%20going%20on%20with%20gay%20abandon%2C%20Bhagwat%20and%20his%20cabal%E2%80%99s%20lips%20were%20sealed.%20The%20clever%20%E2%80%98division%20of%20labour%E2%80%99%20between%20different%20wings%20of%20this%20multi-headed%20hydra%20protec