atic%2C%20secular%20and%20socialist%20nature%20of%20our%20constitution%20is%20under%20severe%20attack%20from%20the%20ideologues%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20stable.%20The%20likes%20of%20JNU%20Vice%20Chancellor%20Shatishir%20Dhulipudi%20are%20arguing%20that%20%E2%80%9CReducing%20India%20to%20a%20civic%20nation%20bound%20by%20a%20constitution%20disregards%20its%20history%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.southasiamonitor.org%2Fspotlight%2Findia-nation-bound-its-constitution-or-selective-interpretation-civilization%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eancient%20heritage%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20culture%20and%20civilization.%20I%20would%20place%20India%20as%20a%20civilisation%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20ideologue%2C%20J.%20Sai%20Deepak%2C%20goes%20on%20to%20argue%20that%20this%20constitution%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20colonialism%2C%20and%20has%20roots%20in%20Christian%20ethos.%20As%20per%20him%2C%20decolonisation%20of%20the%20mind%20is%20essential%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fbooks%2Freviews%2Ftowards-an-idea-of-bharat%2Farticle36681444.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edetach%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fbooks%2Freviews%2Ftowards-an-idea-of-bharat%2Farticle36681444.ece%5C%22%3E%20Indian%20constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20nature%2C%20religion%2C%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20education%20and%20language.%20Importantly%2C%20he%20believes%20that%20thinking%20in%20the%20colonial%20language%20influences%20the%20mind%20towards%20coloniality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20to%20cap%20it%20all%2C%20Bibek%20Debroy%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20(EAC)%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9C%20%E2%80%A6this%20Constitution%20is%20a%20colonial%20legacy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-those-demanding-a-new-constitution-are-fighting-for-a-less-equal-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20questions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20various%20provisions%20of%20the%20same%2C%20particularly%20the%20values%20of%20socialism%2C%20secularism%2C%20justice%2C%20equality%20and%20liberty.%E2%80%9D%20There%20was%20a%20half-hearted%20attempt%20to%20say%20Debroy%20was%20not%20reflecting%20the%20views%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20EAC.%20But%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20that%20this%20is%20what%20Golwalkar%20wanted%20and%20this%20is%20what%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20RSS%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20change%20in%20its%20core%20agenda.%20The%20attempt%20is%20on%20to%20make%20it%20look%20more%20palatable%20to%20all%20and%20sundry.%20While%20some%20of%20the%20panellists%20will%20call%20him%20dated%2C%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20that%20while%20his%20articulation%20may%20be%20dated%2C%20his%20agenda%20is%20dominating%20the%20social%20scene%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696770334000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-100-years-and-the-dark-shadow-of-golwalkars-legacy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20truth%20is%20that%20while%20Golwalkar's%20articulation%20may%20be%20dated%2C%20his%20agenda%20is%20dominating%20the%20social%20scene%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-100-years-and-the-dark-shadow-of-golwalkars-legacy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Super%20Plastronics%20eyes%208%25%20smart%20TV%20market%20share%20in%20next%202%20yrs%3A%20CEO%20Marwah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696768005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2017-08%2F14%2Ffull%2F150265166