di.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40CricCrazyJohns%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20I%20pondered%20on%20how%20easy%20it%20was%20for%20this%20regime%20to%20summon%20celebrities%20to%20pay%20homage%20to%20the%20Vishwaguru%20and%20how%20they%20had%20bartered%20away%20their%20souls%20to%20shake%20hands%20with%20brute%20political%20power%2C%20by%20a%20happy%20stroke%20of%20serendipity%20I%20chanced%20upon%20a%20quote%20from%20the%20great%20Senegalese%20footballer%20Sadio%20Mane%20on%20his%20philosophy%20of%20life.%20In%20his%20own%20stirring%20words%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20resisted%20hunger%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20the%20fields%2C%20I%20survived%20wars%2C%20I%20played%20football%20barefoot%2C%20I%20had%20no%20education%20and%20many%20more%20things%2C%20but%20today%20with%20what%20I%20earn%20from%20football%20I%20can%20help%20my%20people.%20I%20built%20schools%2C%20a%20hospital%2C%20we%20offer%20clothes%2C%20shoes%20food%20to%20people%20living%20in%20extreme%20poverty.%20In%20addition%2C%20I%20give%2070%20euros%20per%20month%20to%20all%20people%20in%20a%20very%20poor%20region%20of%20Senegal.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20flaunt%20fancy%20cars%2C%20fancy%20villas%2C%20travel%2C%20let%20alone%20planes.%20I%E2%80%99d%20rather%20have%20my%20people%20get%20a%20bit%20of%20what%20life%20has%20given%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6my%20people%20get%20a%20bit%20of%20what%20life%20has%20given%20me.%E2%80%9D%20What%20a%20stark%20contrast%20from%20our%20famous%20persons%20who%20are%20so%20consumed%20in%20themselves%20and%20busy%20cashing%20in%20on%20their%20demigod%20status%20that%20they%20have%20forgotten%20that%20they%20owe%20a%20debt%20to%20society.%20It%20is%20sad%20because%20celebrities%20are%20respected%20community%20mentors%20with%20a%20greater%20influence%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20young%2C%20than%20religious%20or%20political%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENobody%20expects%20them%20to%20part%20with%20their%20money.%20But%2C%20like%20the%20great%20West%20Indian%2C%20Michael%20Holding%20observed%2C%20after%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfun%20and%20games%E2%80%9D%2C%20celebrities%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20use%20their%20privileged%20position%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20not%20about%20the%20laurels%20won%20but%20what%20you%20give%20back%20to%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJoseph%20Campbell%20put%20it%20best%20with%20his%20simple%20but%20profound%20assertion%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20hero%20is%20someone%20who%20has%20given%20his%20or%20her%20life%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20oneself%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20celebrity%20has%20generally%20been%20reticent%2C%20if%20not%20downright%20uncaring%20of%20his%20social%20responsibilities.%20I%20had%20a%20theory%2C%20now%20dented%20by%20Mane%2C%20that%20the%20poorer%20a%20nation%2C%20the%20more%20solipsistic%20and%20self-seeking%20are%20its%20rich%20and%20famous%2C%20possibly%20because%20of%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20insecurity.%20Amid%20conspicuous%20and%20widespread%20deprivation%2C%20our%20celebrities%20tend%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20misery%20by%20bolting%20their%20ivory%20tower.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20celebrities%20wield%20incredible%20social%20power.%20With%20millions%20of%20devotees%20hanging%20on%20to%20their%20every%20word%2C%20they%20are%20up%20there%20with%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leading%20opinion-makers.%20They%20can%20invigorate%20social%20justice%20campaigns%20with%20the%20power%20of%20their%20voices.%20Regrettably%2C%20most%20of%20them%20are%20self-obsessive.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Tendulkar.%20The%20greatest%20run%20getter%20in%20history%2C%20arguably%20the%20richest%20cricketer%2C%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20masses%2C%20Sachin%20has%20exploited%20his%20stardom%20solely%20for%20hawking%20merchandise%20and%20for%20other%20less%20honourable%20purposes.%20He%20sought%20and%20obtained%20a%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20customs%20duty%20exemption%20on%20the%20Ferrari%20presented%20to%20him%20by%20Michael%20Schumacher%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ferrari%20company.%20More%20controversially%2C%20he%20allegedly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Fdrdo-officer-files-cbi-complaint-on-sanjay-narang-resort-sachin-tendulkar-denies-economic-interest%2Farticleshow%2F53291570.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etried%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20procurer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20his%20hotelier%20crony%20who%20had%20illegally%20encroached%20army%20cantonment%20land%2C%20but%20the%20then%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20Manohar%20Parrikar%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20play%20ball.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Sachin%20goes%20missing%20when%20it%20matters.%20He%20remained%20silent%20when%20the%20female%20wrestlers%20protesting%20sexual%20harassment%20sought%20his%20backing%2C%20and%20he%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20his%20former%20teammate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-jaffer-uttarakhand-coach-cricket-communalism%5C%22%3EWassim%20Jaffer%2C%20who%20was%20unjustly%20accused%20of%20communal%20bias%20by%20right-wing%20bigots%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whereas%20Anil%20Kumble%20showed%20character%20by%20coming%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Jaffer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-jaffer-uttarakhand-cricket-communal-good-muslim%5C%22%3EWasim%20Jaffer%20and%20the%20Futile%20Pursuit%20of%20Being%20a%20%E2%80%98Good%20Muslim%E2%80%99%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20charge%20that%20Sachin%20is%20indifferent%20to%20the%20social%20problems%20of%20the%20country%2C%20his%20apologists%20claim%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Capolitical%E2%80%9D.%20How%20then%20do%20they%20explain%20his%20government-tutored%20response%20to%20the%20tweets%20of%20Rihanna%20and%20Greta%20Thunberg%20in%20support%20of%20our%20farmers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnabashedly%20playing%20toady%20to%20this%20regime%2C%20Tendulkar%20used%20mighty%20words%2C%20calling%20on%20all%20Indians%20%E2%80%9Cto%20resist%20any%20threat%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20by%20external%20forces.%E2%80%9D%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20bit%20rich!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20two%20other%20mega%20superstars%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20have%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20shutting%20themselves%20off%20in%20their%20luxurious%20cocoons%2C%20ignoring%20the%20life%20and%20death%20problems%20of%20the%20country%20and%20the%20shrinking%20democratic%20space.%20They%20finally%20spoke%20up%20some%20months%20ago%20in%20Kolkata.%20Amitabh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Famitabh-bachchan-and-shah-rukh-khan-speak-up-modestly-but-its-still-welcome%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520went%2520on%2520to%2520say%2Cjingoism%2520along%2520with%2520moral%2520policing%25E2%2580%25A6%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ementioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20current%20brand%20of%20historical%20couched%20in%20fictionalised%20jingoism%2C%20along%20with%20moral%20policing%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20about%20questions%20being%20raised%20on%20civil%20liberties%20and%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20Khan%20talked%20of%20cinema%20as%20a%20medium%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20humanity%E2%80%99s%20intense%20capacity%20for%20compassion%2C%20unity%20and%20brotherhood.%E2%80%9D%20A%20trifle%2C%20pussyfooted%20and%20oblique%2C%20but%20as%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20a%20penny%20is%20better%20than%20none!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20experience%20I%20know%20that%20our%20women%20are%20infinitely%20smarter%20than%20men%20and%20made%20of%20sterner%20stuff.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-media-wrestlers-protest-brij-bhushan-singh%5C%22%3Emonths-long%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20of%20our%20internationally%20renowned%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20led%20by%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20against%20continual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpictures-phone-location-other-evidence-show-brij-bhushan-allegedly-making-advances%5C%22%3Esexual%20harassment%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20most%20courageous%20face-off%20by%20women%20anywhere%20against%20a%20repressive%2C%20hostile%20government%20that%20used%20every%20sordid%20means%20to%20bring%20them%20to%20their%20knees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20despite%20coercive%20police%20brutality%2C%20waves%20of%20officially%20sponsored%20vandalism%20of%20their%20protest%20site%2C%20intimidation%2C%20harassment%20and%20vicious%20slander%2C%20these%20indomitable%20women%20stood%20their%20ground%2C%20eventually%20forcing%20this%20regime%20to%20initiate%20legal%20action%20against%20one%20of%20its%20own.%20By%20throwing%20down%20the%20gauntlet%20against%20a%20deeply%20ingrained%2C%20rotten%20culture%20of%20patriarchy%2C%20they%20spoke%20up%20for%20all%20the%20voiceless%20girls%20who%20cannot%20protect%20themselves.%20Their%20groundbreaking%20protest%20has%20forged%20an%20indelible%20legacy%20that%20will%20inspire%20all%20women.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20bleak%20time%20when%20our%20freedoms%20are%20under%20attack%2C%20comparisons%20are%20inevitably%20drawn%20with%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20the%20Emergency.%20Of%20yesteryears%E2%80%99%20Bollywood%20stars%2C%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20who%20would%20have%20turned%20100%20on%20September%2025%20this%20year%2C%20was%20the%20lone%20celebrity%20with%20the%20spine%20and%20moral%20compass%20to%20publicly%20express%20his%20dissent%20in%20the%20dire%20period%20of%20the%20Emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fsrk-i-hear-you-and-so-does-everyone-else%5C%22%3ESRK%2C%20I%20Hear%20You.%20And%20So%20Does%20Everyone%20Else.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20to%20say%20a%20few%20words%20in%20appreciation%20of%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ogre%20in%20that%20fascist%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20Dev%20Anand%20flatly%20refused%2C%20describing%20his%20own%20audacity%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20call%20to%20conscience%E2%80%9D.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20his%20films%20were%20banned%20on%20TV%20and%20All%20India%20Radio%20proscribed%20any%20reference%20to%20his%20name.%20Unfazed%2C%20during%20an%20election%20rally%20of%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20Jayprakash%20Narayan%2C%20he%20delivered%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20The%20evergreen%20screen%20idol%20was%2C%20in%20truth%2C%20a%20real-life%20hero!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20any%20discussion%20on%20our%20celebrity%20world%20would%20be%20incomplete%20if%20it%20does%20not%20include%20the%20celebrity%20nonpareil%20%E2%80%93%20our%20ace%20politician%20and%20multifaceted%20supreme%20leader.%20The%20consummate%20purveyor%20of%20illusions%20and%20dreams%2C%20he%20has%20become%20all%20things%20to%20his%20people%20%E2%80%93%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20fashion%20model%2C%20tear-jerking%20thespian%2C%20religious%20leader%2C%20historian%20and%20even%20war%20strategist.%20He%20has%20had%20an%20overpowering%20influence%20on%20our%20society%2C%20a%20power%20that%20is%20almost%20deific%20in%20the%20religious%20frenzy%20that%20he%20invokes%20in%20his%20Bhakts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20celebrities%20are%20to%20be%20ranked%20by%20the%20extent%20of%20their%20influence%20on%20society%20%E2%80%93%20for%20good%20or%20evil%20%E2%80%93%20then%20our%20supreme%20leader%20stands%20peerless%20at%20the%20pinnacle%2C%20the%20dominant%20personality%20of%20our%20time.%20He%20has%20artfully%20exploited%20the%20unthinking%20credulity%20of%20his%20people%20and%20the%20fragility%20of%20our%20democratic%20institutions%20to%20set%20himself%20up%20as%20the%20ultimate%20arbiter%20of%20our%20country%2C%20impacting%20our%20society%20in%C2%A0%20indelible%20ways.%20The%20nine-year%20saga%20of%20menacing%20majoritarianism%2C%20hare-brained%20schemes%20and%20pure%20malevolence%20has%20left%20us%20a%20splintered%20nation%20full%20of%20hatred%2C%20cruelty%20and%20rage.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20terrifying%20legacy%20for%20future%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696761309000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F08153339%2F1885944-modi-1547197401.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhen-celebrities-bow-down-to-the-regime%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfun%20and%20games%E2%80%9D%2C%20celebrities%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20use%20their%20privileged%20position%20to%20make%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A228%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwhen-celebrities-bow-down-to-the-regime%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20clears%20appointments%20of%2012%20executive%20directors%20for%20state-owned%20banks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696759808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-07%2F10%2Ffull%2F1657469296-2194.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fgovt-clears-appointments-of-12-executive-directors-for-state-owned-banks-123100800497_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20approved%20the%20appointments%20of%2012%20general%20managers%20as%20executive%20directors%20(EDs)%20of%20various%20public%20sector%20banks%20(PSBs)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fgovt-clears-appointments-of-12-executive-directors-for-state-owned-banks-123100800497_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fgovt-clears-appointments-of-12-executive-directors-for-state-owned-banks-123100800497_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Fgovt-clears-appointments-of-12-executive-directors-for-state-owned-banks-123100800497_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MCX%20gets%20Sebi%20approval%20to%20launch%20new%20commodity%20derivatives%20platform%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696759007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F29%2Ffull%2F1695963781-8564.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmcx-gets-sebi-approval-to-launch-new-commodity-derivatives-platform-123100800490_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MCX%20had%20initially%20intended%20to%20introduce%20the%20CDP%20on%20October%203.%20However%2C%20they%20have%20not%20revealed%20the%20new%20launch%20date%20yet%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmcx-gets-sebi-approval-to-launch-new-commodity-derivatives-platform-123100800490_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ossification%20Test%20of%20a%20Juvenile%20Declared%20as%20Adult%20on%20the%20Date%20of%20the%20Crime%3A%20SC%20Stays%20HP%20HC%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20On%20Friday%2C%20October%206%2C%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20comprising%20Justices%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Rajesh%20Bindal%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2023%2F33467%2F33467_2023_12_35_47433_Order_06-Oct-2023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJoginder%20Pal%20vs%20The%20State%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Estayed%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20dated%20April%2026%2C%202023%2C%20setting%20aside%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20court%20below%20that%20the%20accused%20be%20treated%20as%20major%20and%20be%20tried%20accordingly.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20also%20ordered%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fsci-tech%2F2023%2F02%2F15%2Fossification-test-your-age-is-in-your-bones.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThis%2520test%2520involves%2520examining%2520x%2Cuntil%2520the%2520end%2520of%2520adolescence.%5C%22%3Eossification%20test%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20accused%20to%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%2C%20and%20depending%20upon%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Testing%20Authority%2C%20dealing%20with%20the%20accused%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20(JJB)%20held%20the%20murder-accused%20in%20a%20road%20rage%20case%20to%20be%20a%20juvenile%20on%20September%2019%2C%202014%2C%20finding%20his%20age%20below%2018%20years%20of%20age%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20June%2020%2C%202014.%20The%20father%20of%20the%20deceased%20challenged%20the%20JJB%E2%80%99s%20order%20before%20the%20Court%20of%20Sessions%20Judge%2C%20Mandi%20(Himachal%20Pradesh)%20which%20allowed%20the%20appeal%2C%20setting%20aside%20JJB%E2%80%99s%20order%20with%20a%20direction%20to%20make%20an%20inquiry%20for%20determination%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20thereafter%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20matter%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20another%20order%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20JJB%20on%20May%2026%2C%202017%2C%20again%20finding%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused%20to%20be%20below%2018%20years%2C%20and%20he%20was%20declared%20as%20juvenile%20in%20conflict%20with%20law.%20The%20father%20of%20the%20deceased%20again%20assailed%20the%20order%20by%20way%20of%20an%20appeal%2C%20and%20in%20terms%20of%20judgment%20dated%20February%2028%2C%202018%2C%20the%20appellate%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20JJB%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20and%20issued%20directions%20to%20make%20a%20fresh%20inquiry%20for%20determination%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20to%20proceed%20with%20the%20matter%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Shiv%20Kumar%20alias%20Shivam%2C%20filed%20a%20criminal%20revision%20petition%20before%20the%20high%20court%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20not%20heard%20by%20the%20appellate%20court%20before%20passing%20the%20order%20on%20February%2028%2C%202018.%20The%20high%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20order%20of%20the%20appellate%20court%2C%20directing%20it%20to%20hear%20the%20matter%20afresh%20after%20hearing%20the%20accused.%20Upon%20remand%2C%20the%20appellate%20court%20again%20set%20aside%20the%20JJB%E2%80%99s%20order%20dated%20May%2026%2C%202017%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20Board%20to%20make%20an%20inquiry%20for%20determination%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20challenged%20this%20judgment%20by%20way%20of%20a%20criminal%20revision%20petition%20before%20the%20high%20court%20which%20set%20aside%20the%20findings%20returned%20by%20the%20appellate%20court%20on%20April%2024%2C%202019%2C%20with%20a%20direction%20to%20decide%20the%20appeal%20strictly%20in%20accordance%20with%20law.%20On%20November%2020%2C%202021%2C%20the%20appellate%20court%20again%20set%20aside%20the%20JJB%E2%80%99s%20order%20and%20held%20the%20accused%20to%20be%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacts%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20deceased%20alleged%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20the%20date%20of%20birth%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20mentioned%20in%20the%20matriculation%20certificate%20as%20June%2014%2C%201997.%20Section%2049%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Frepealed-act%2Frepealed_act_documents%2FA2000-56.pdf%5C%22%3EJuvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202000%3C%2Fa%3E%20lays%20down%20that%20where%20it%20appears%20to%20the%20competent%20authority%20that%20person%20brought%20before%20it%20under%20any%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20this%20Act%20is%20a%20juvenile%20or%20the%20child%2C%20it%20shall%20make%20due%20inquiry%20so%20as%20to%20the%20age%20of%20person%20so%20brought%20before%20it%2C%20which%20shall%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20the%20true%20age%20of%20that%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20Rule%2012.3%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Rule%2C%202007%2C%20the%20age%20determination%20inquiry%20is%20to%20be%20conducted%20by%20the%20Court%20or%20the%20Board%20or%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be%2C%20the%20Committee%20by%20seeking%20evidence%20by%20obtaining%20matriculation%20or%20equivalent%20certificates%2C%20if%20available%2C%20and%20in%20the%20absence%20whereof%2C%20the%20date%20of%20birth%20certificate%20from%20the%20school%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20argued%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20since%20the%20matriculation%20certificate%20of%20the%20accused%20was%20available%2C%20the%20date%20mentioned%20therein%20was%20to%20be%20construed%20as%20sacrosanct%2C%20and%20this%20was%20lost%20sight%20of%20by%20the%20appellate%20court%20while%20allowing%20the%20appeal.%20It%20was%20urged%20that%20the%20appellate%20court%20did%20not%20appreciate%20that%20the%20factum%20of%20date%20of%20birth%20of%20the%20accused%20being%20June%2014%2C%201997%2C%20it%20was%20also%20corroborated%20by%20other%20documents%2C%20Aadhaar%20Card%2C%20voter%20card%20and%20school%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20argued%20before%20the%20high%20court%20that%20there%20was%20some%20discrepancy%20with%20regard%20to%20name%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20as%20his%20name%20is%20Shivam%20Chaudhary%20and%20not%20Shiv%20Kumar%20and%20the%20documents%20relied%20upon%20by%20the%20appellate%20court%20were%20relating%20to%20Shiv%20Kumar%20and%20not%20the%20accused%2C%20whose%20name%20is%20Shivam%20Chaudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20deceased%2C%20who%20is%20a%20respondent%20in%20the%20case%2C%20submitted%20to%20the%20high%20court%20that%20there%20is%20a%20variation%20in%20the%20date%20of%20birth%20of%20the%20accused%20as%20recorded%20in%20the%20matriculation%20certificate%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20record%20of%20the%20school%20and%20the%20record%20of%20the%20Gram%20Panchayat.%20Besides%2C%20it%20has%20been%20alleged%20that%20criminal%20proceedings%20stand%20initiated%20against%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20accused%20as%20also%20the%20school%20management%20for%20forging%20with%20the%20admission%20record%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20found%20that%20the%20appellate%20court%20had%20not%20taken%20into%20consideration%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20documents%20in%20which%20date%20of%20birth%20of%20the%20accused%20is%20June%2014%2C%201997%20were%20existing%20before%20the%20date%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20so%20it%20cannot%20be%20assumed%20that%20there%20was%20some%20tinkering%20with%20the%20date%20of%20birth%20therein%2C%20so%20that%20the%20accused%20could%20be%20shown%20as%20a%20minor%20after%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20relied%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgment%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F190473838%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERishipal%20Singh%20Solanki%20vs%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2021)%20and%20others%20in%20which%2C%20it%20was%20held%20that%20Section%2094%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fhandle%2F123456789%2F2148%3Fsam_handle%3D123456789%2F1362%5C%22%3EJuvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015%20%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20akin%20to%20Section%2049%20of%20the%202000%20Act%20raises%20a%20presumption%20regarding%20juvenility%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20child%20brought%20before%20the%20JJB%20or%20the%20Committee.%20However%2C%20in%20case%20the%20Board%20or%20Committee%20has%20reasonable%20ground%20for%20doubt%2C%20it%20can%20undertake%20the%20process%20of%20determination%20of%20age%20by%20seeking%20evidence.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20held%20that%20the%20presumption%20has%20to%20be%20drawn%20on%20observation%20of%20the%20child.%20The%20evidence%20can%20be%20in%20the%20form%20of%20date%20of%20birth%20certificate%20from%20the%20school%20or%20the%20matriculation%20certificate%20from%20the%20Board%20concerned%2C%20if%20available.%20In%20the%20absence%20thereof%2C%20the%20birth%20certificate%20given%20by%20a%20Corporation%20or%20by%20a%20Municipal%20Authority%20or%20a%20Panchayat%20can%20be%20relied%20upon.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20above%2C%20the%20age%20has%20to%20be%20determined%20by%20an%20ossification%20test%20or%20any%20other%20medical%20age%20determination%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20held%20that%20ossification%20test%20will%20put%20to%20rest%20any%20controversy%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused%20as%20on%20the%20date%20when%20the%20offence%20took%20place%20and%20the%20test%20would%20carry%20more%20authenticity%20in%20the%20light%20of%20there%20being%20documents%20which%20are%20giving%20contradictory%20dates%20of%20the%20age%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20found%20that%20whereas%20there%20is%20no%20tinkering%20with%20the%20documents%20in%20terms%20whereof%20the%20accused%20was%20a%20major%20as%20on%20the%20date%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20there%20is%20an%20overwriting%20etc%20in%20some%20of%20the%20documents%2C%20benefit%20of%20which%20is%20being%20claimed%20by%20the%20accused%20to%20put%20forth%20his%20contention%20that%20he%20was%20a%20minor%20on%20the%20date%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696758024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fossification-test-of-a-juvenile-declared-as-adult-on-the-date-of-the-crime-sc-stays-hp-hc-order%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Determination%20by%20the%20courts%20of%20the%20age%20of%20juveniles%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law%20continues%20to%20be%20problematic%2C%20with%20evidence%20proving%20to%20be%20doubtful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fossification-test-of-a-juvenile-declared-as-adult-on-the-date-of-the-crime-sc-stays-hp-hc-order%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Policeman%20shoots%20dead%20two%20Israelis%20at%20Egyptian%20tourist%20site%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696756800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-pompey-pillar-sphinx_6313622.jpg%3F20231008103942%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpoliceman-shoots-dead-two-israelis-at-egyptian-tourist-site-in-alexandria-local-media-12979928%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20two%20Israelis%20and%20one%20Egyptian%20have%20been%20killed%20after%20a%20policeman%20opened%20fire%20on%20a%20group%20of%20tourists%20in%20Alexandria%2C%20a