(ICSE)%20by%20the%20Mobius%20Foundation%20saw%20educators%20helping%20students%20bring%20their%20unique%20eco-friendly%20ideas%20to%20fruition%2C%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20few%20startups%2C%20and%20over%2015%20countries%20coming%20together%20for%20collective%20action%20against%20climate%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Doctor%E2%80%99s%20AI-Powered%20Mobile%20Tool%20Screens%20%26amp%3B%20Detects%20Tuberculosis%20In%20a%20Few%20Seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20concerns%20in%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F97795%2Fvolunteering-india-developingcountry-travelling-voluntourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20is%20Tuberculosis.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20approximately%2010%20million%20people%20fall%20ill%20yearly%20with%20infectious%20diseases.%20However%2C%20only%206%20million%20cases%20are%20identified%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%204%20million%20being%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they%20are%20either%20undiagnosed%2C%20untreated%20or%20go%20unreported%20to%20the%20healthcare%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20TB%20cases%20among%20children%20less%20than%2015%20years%20in%20India%20estimated%20to%20be%203%2C42%2C000%20every%20year%2C%20the%20detection%20of%20only%201%2C35%2C734%20children%20in%202022%20would%20mean%20that%20over%202%2C00%2C000%20(60%25)%20children%20with%20TB%20were%20missed%20last%20year%20alone.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20underlines%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20Dr%20Arun%20Chowdary%20Kotaru%2C%20a%20seasoned%20consultant%20in%20Respiratory%2FPulmonology%20and%20Sleep%20Medicine%20at%20the%20Artemis%20Hospital%2C%20Gurgaon%2C%20provides%20insight%20into%20this%20issue%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CMany%20patients%20go%20undiagnosed%20or%20%E2%80%98missing%E2%80%99%20because%20the%20traditional%20testing%20system%20takes%20weeks%20to%20produce%20results%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20reach%20patients%20promptly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20crucial%20time%20lag%20between%20testing%20and%20receiving%20test%20results%2C%20a%20Pune-based%20startup%20called%20DeepTek%20has%20developed%20a%20technology%20claiming%20to%20identify%20tuberculosis%20cases%20within%20seconds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Amit%20Kharat%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20DeepTek%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20patients%20undergo%20an%20X-ray%2C%20our%20AI-based%20model%2C%20Genki%2C%20scans%20the%20reports%20and%20identifies%20any%20signs%20of%20TB%20(abnormalities)%20within%2030%20to%2060%20seconds.%20Radiologists%20can%20then%20thoroughly%20review%20the%20reports%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20infection%2C%20a%20process%20that%20previously%20would%20have%20taken%20weeks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20remarkable%20potential%20of%20this%20technology%2C%20we%20had%20a%20bunch%20of%20questions%20regarding%20its%20function.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20clarified%20all%20our%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAiming%20to%20make%20India%20TB%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20major%20concerns%20that%20arose%20when%20our%20conversation%20with%20Dr%20Amit%20began%20were%20%E2%80%93%20How%20does%20the%20technology%20work%3F%20What%20is%20its%20accuracy%3F%20And%20how%20can%20it%20reach%20the%20last%20mile%20in%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnswering%20how%20the%20technology%20works%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20started%20researching%20on%20how%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20can%20be%20used%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284072%2Fsynapsica-radiologist-ai-mri-technology-imaging-accurate-report-diagnoses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efield%20of%20radiology%2C%20I%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20TB%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%20and%20the%20government%20is%20looking%20for%20new-age%20solutions%20to%20eliminate%20this%20disease.%20This%20is%20how%20our%20journey%20started%20in%20the%20TB%20scanning%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20AI%20was%20developed%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-5-1696427075-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331550%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20AI%20was%20developed%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20DeepTek%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20stigma%20around%20TB%20and%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20patients%20do%20not%20come%20to%20doctors%20till%20their%20illness%20becomes%20very%20serious.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20since%20the%20disease%20spreads%20through%20cough%20droplets%2C%20the%20patient%20has%20most%20likely%20affected%20more%20people%20in%20the%20area.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20reaches%20these%20areas%20to%20scan%20for%20more%20cases%20of%20TB.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20camps%20set%20up%20and%20vans%20reach%20rural%20areas%20to%20do%20X-rays%20of%20these%20people.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20X-ray%20is%20done%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20a%20radiology%20department%20for%20study.%20This%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20reach%20the%20suspected%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20where%20Genki%20comes%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20chest%20X-rays%20are%20scanned%20by%20the%20AI%20and%20within%20seconds%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20CPU%20setting%20and%20core%20capacity%20of%20the%20system%20in%20the%20van%2C%20camp%20or%20hospital%2C%20the%20reports%20come%20in%20within%2060%20seconds.%20This%20way%20the%20patient%20can%20be%20informed%20and%20taken%20to%20treatment%20then%20and%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20sputum%20test%20can%20be%20done%20to%20confirm%20the%20presence%20of%20infection%20in%20the%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20what%20used%20to%20happen%20was%20that%20once%20the%20patient%20was%20diagnosed%2C%20a%20healthcare%20worker%20deported%20by%20the%20government%20would%20find%20them%20and%20then%20take%20them%20for%20further%20testing.%20This%20would%20cost%20the%20government%20unnecessary%20expenses.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20the%20suspected%20cases%20had%20to%20undergo%20a%20Genexpert%20Test%20after%20an%20X-ray%20which%20is%20a%20costly%20affair%20for%20the%20government.%20Now%2C%20with%20Genki%2C%20not%20every%20patient%20has%20to%20go%20through%20the%20test%20but%20only%20the%20ones%20detected%20by%20the%20AI%20have%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20not%20only%20reduced%20the%20time%20lag%20between%20testing%20and%20results%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20cost%20for%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20its%20accuracy%2C%20Amit%20explains%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199904%2Fmumbai-startup-tb-artificial-intelligence-innovation-tuberculosis-diagnosis-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20AI%20was%20developed%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20more%20than%2010%20million%20data%20points%20from%20various%20sources%20and%20places%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChest%20X-ray%20data%20points%20are%20easily%20available%20for%20research%20purposes.%20We%20have%20also%20collaborated%20with%20medical%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20for%20research%20and%20collecting%20data.%20We%20have%20been%20audited%20by%20Stop%20TB%2C%20a%20WHO%20body%20which%20has%20given%20a%20green%20signal%20calling%20our%20AI%E2%80%99s%20results%20as%20good%20as%20human%20reading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20838px)%20100vw%2C%20838px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Amit%20Kharat%20and%20Dr%20Ajit%20Patel%2C%20co-founders%20of%20DeepTek%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-7-1696427069-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Amit%20Kharat%20and%20Dr%20Ajit%20Patel%2C%20co-founders%20of%20DeepTek.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20DeepTek%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20was%20initially%20used%20in%20Greater%20Chennai%20Corporation%20and%20has%20expanded%20to%208%20districts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20screened%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20patients%20in%20totality.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20have%20moved%20to%20Puducherry%20and%20Thane%20municipal%20corporation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20India%2C%20AI%20is%20working%20in%20countries%20like%20Bangladesh%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Mongolia%2C%20and%20Thailand.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20approval%20from%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%E2%80%99s%20FDA%20and%20we%20recently%20received%20approval%20from%20an%20Indian%20regulatory%20body%20called%20Central%20Drugs%20Standard%20Control%20Organisation%20(CDSCO)%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20Genki%20can%20help%20the%20government%20reach%20the%20remotest%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20and%20eliminate%20TB%2C%20Dr%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20newer%20innovations%2C%20the%20X-ray%20machines%20have%20become%20so%20small%20and%20easy%20to%20carry%20that%20a%20person%20can%20take%20it%20to%20the%20remotest%20of%20places.%20Combined%20with%20Genki%2C%20any%20nodal%20officer%20can%20easily%20locate%20patients%20and%20get%20their%20sputum%20samples.%20All%20this%20can%20be%20done%20with%20a%20push%20of%20a%20few%20buttons.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeeptek%20started%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F59851%2Ftuberculosis-xdr-10-km-ru