ping%2C%20and%20I%20was%20unsure%20about%20my%20career.%20Seeing%20my%20friends%20studying%20or%20working%20on%20social%20media%20led%20me%20further%20down%20the%20spiral.%20After%20three%20months%20postpartum%2C%20I%20started%20having%20suicidal%20thoughts%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now%2027-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20night%2C%20she%20poured%20out%20her%20feelings%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20cried.%20Her%20mother%20suggested%20that%20she%20should%20start%20therapy%2C%20which%20effectively%20turned%20around%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20life.%20The%20therapy%20had%20such%20a%20transformational%20effect%20on%20this%20Chennai%20resident%E2%80%99s%20life%20that%20today%2C%20she%20runs%20a%20mental%20wellness%20startup%20called%20%E2%80%98The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%98cafe%20for%20mental%20health%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLove%20and%20hope%20drive%20everything%20we%20do.%20We%20want%20to%20bring%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20(self-love)%20and%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Therapy%20changed%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pooja%20started%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%2C%20a%20mental%20wellness%20space%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-1-1696427267-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove