n.%20It%20really%20helped.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20realise%20many%20more%20things%20about%20myself%20and%20I%20am%20able%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20failures%20better.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPooja%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20stigma%20around%20mental%20health.%20To%20bridge%20that%20gap%2C%20in%202019%2C%20she%20started%20an%20NGO%20called%20Transfomind%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20an%20online%20platform%20to%20create%20awareness%20of%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20collaborated%20with%20mental%20health%20experts%20to%20develop%20educational%20material%20on%20mental%20well-being.%20This%20idea%20gained%20traction%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20raising%20significant%20awareness.%20In%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20teamed%20up%20with%20Montfort%20College%20to%20offer%20free%20therapy%20sessions%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20businesswoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20also%20a%20challenging%20time%20in%20Pooja%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life%20as%20she%20was%20separated%20from%20her%20husband.%20During%20a%20solo%20trip%2C%20a%20conversation%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20mental%20health%20ignited%20the%20fire%20in%20the%2027-year-old%20to%20do%20something%20more%20concrete%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20little%20bit%20of%20love%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20hope%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20therapy%20spaces%20at%20The%20Love%20Hope%20Company%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-company-2-1696427268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FLove-hope-