C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epollution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20the%20time%20most%20parents%20realise%20it%2C%20it%20becomes%20very%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20rectify%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20realisation%20occurred%20to%2038-year-old%20Pruthvi%20Gowda%20when%20he%20became%20father%20to%20his%20baby%20boy.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20that%20no%20parent%20can%20deny%20is%20that%20kids%20grow%20out%20of%20things%20at%20a%20very%20fast%20rate.%20While%20we%20might%20pass%20down%20certain%20things%20to%20cousins%20and%20siblings%2C%20most%20of%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20products%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%20later%20gave%20birth%20to%20Gro%20Club%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F77487%2Fbengaluru-startup-eco-friendly-wedding-cards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru-based%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20created%20a%20circular%20economy%20by%20lending%20baby-use%20products%20on%20a%20subscription%20basis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20memories%20while%20being%20sustainable%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20January%202022%2C%20and%20currently%20operable%20only%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20company%20has%20received%20an%20overwhelming%20response%20from%20parents%20dealing%20with%20similar%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPruthvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20marketing%20industry%20for%20some%20time%2C%20I%20had%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%20Gro%20Club%20is%20a%20passion%20project%20as%20it%20marries%20both%20sustainability%20and%20entrepreneurship.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20idea%20of%20Gro%20Club%20brewed%2C%20Pruthvi%20turned%20towards%20his%20friends%20Hrishikesh%20H%20S%2C%20Roopesh%20Shah%20and%20Sapna%20M%20S%20for%20support.%20%E2%80%9CHrishikesh%20and%20I%20worked%20together%20on%20my%20previous%20venture%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20his%20dream%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFour%20of%20us%20are%20parents%20of%20kids%20between%205%20and%2014%20years%20of%20age.%20They%20could%20relate%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20them%20outgrowing%20things%20too.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20all%20of%20us%20believed%20that%20with%20our%20startup%2C%20we%20could%20pitch-in%20and%20reduce%20the%20mounting%20trash%20in%20the%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETerming%20products%20such%20as%20bicycles%2C%20cribs%2C%20bunk%20beds%20and%20strollers%20as%20single-use%20products%2C%20Pruthvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20products%20are%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20investment%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20startup%20was%20founded%20by%20four%20friends%20in%202022.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fgrowclub-1-1696341835-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331440%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20founders%20of%20Gro%20Club%20%E2%80%94%20Pruthvi%20Gowda%2C%20Hrishikesh%20H%20S%2C%20Roopesh%20Shah%20and%20Sapna%20M%20S.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Pruthvi%20Gowda%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecycling%2C%20reusing%20and%20creating%20a%20circular%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20carbon%20release%20in%20producing%20these%20products%20is%20also%20quite%20high.%20%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20example%20of%20bicycles%2C%20for%20instance.%20To%20produce%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20bicycle%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20carbon%20released%20is%20close%20to%20330%20kgs.%20This%20cycle%20then%2C%20after%20some%20rounds%20of%20use%20ends%20up%20in%20dumpsters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20when%20a%20person%20subscribes%20to%20a%20cycle%20from%20Gro%20Club%2C%20they%20are%20consciously%20deciding%20not%20to%20add%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311459%2Fpad-care-labs-safe-disposal-of-sanitary-pads-cuts-carbon-converts-into-packaging-ajinkya-dhariya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarbon%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20atmosphere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20business%20works%2C%20Pruthvi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20only%20pay%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20actual%20cost%20of%20the%20product%20in%20subscriptions%20and%20also%20take%20a%20step%20towards%20sustainable%20living.%20The%20products%20are%20therefore%20reused%20but%20not%20second-hand.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20products%20that%20we%20have%20are%20manufactured%20by%20us%20initially%20and%20are%20refurbished%20for%20every%20new%20user.%20The%20process%20of%20refurbishing%20renews%20the%20product%20and%20does%20not%20cause%20as%20much%20carbon%20emission%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCeNnwHzFF05