ur%2C%20they%20would%20not%20return%20without%20having%20%3Cem%3Erabri%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20our%20shop%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20the%20iconic%20eatery%20makes%20up%20to%20150%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%20every%20day.%20Sold%20for%20two%20%3Cem%3Eanas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Back%20then%2C%20anas%20were%20a%20form%20of%20currency%20and%2016%20anas%20makes%201%20Re)%20earlier%2C%20today%2C%20the%20sweet%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%20500%20per%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20rate%20of%20the%20sweet%20otherwise%20is%20Rs%20360-400%20per%20kg.%20Other%20than%20%3Cem%3Erabri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20family%20introduced%20several%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20sweets%20like%20%3Cem%3Emoong%20thal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egulab%20chakri%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekalakand%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emaal%20puvey%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20typical%20Rajasthani%20thali%20with%20bejad%20ki%20roti%2C%20aloo%20pyaaz%20paneer%20sabzi%2C%20gatte%20ki%20sabzi%2C%20dal%20tadka%2C%20mirchi%20ke%20Tipore%2C%20lehsun%20chutney%2C%20and%20raita.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMahaveer-Rabri-Bhandaar-1-1696338562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20typical%20Rajasthani%20thali%20with%20%3Cem%3Ebejad%20ki%20roti%2C%20aloo%20pyaaz%20paneer%20sabzi%2C%20gatte%20ki%20sabzi%2C%20dal%20tadka%2C%20mirchi%20ke%20Tipore%2C%20lehsun%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eraita%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20their%20regular%20diners%2C%20Kartik%20Bhargava%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20uncle%20took%20me%20there%20for%20the%20first%20time%20a%20few%20years%20back.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20and%20I%20visit%20the%20eatery%20whenever%20we%20have%20time.%20It%20became%20our%20bonding%20spot.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302156%2Fjaipur-sisters-quit-job-to-turn-ancestral-home-into-vintage-cafe-obaque%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeateries%20in%20Jaipur%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20provide%20the%20same%20food%20but%20no%20one%20can%20beat%20the%20authentic%20taste%20that%20Mahaveer%20Rabri%20Bhandar%20offers.%20They%20must%20have%20some%20secret%20ingredient%20that%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20all%20other%20copies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20numerous%20outlets%20in%20Jaipur%20with%20names%20that%20sound%20similar%20to%20Mahaveer%20Rabri%20Bhandar%20but%20Deepak%20says%20that%20their%20quality%20is%20their%20USP%20that%20attracts%20diverse%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20an%20honour%20to%20take%20the%20family%20legacy%20forward.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20my%20son%2C%20who%20is%20in%20class%2012%2C%20wishes%20to%20pursue%20hotel%20management%20and%20aims%20to%20join%20the%20business.%20It%20gives%20me%20immense%20satisfaction%20that%20this%20legacy%20will%20continue%20even%20after%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20